      "message": "I realize that, it\u0027s just that returning from inside this block will bite someone later. It would be better to just do this like\n\n    if (f1.empty() {\n        SkDebugf(\"F1 is empty\\n\");\n    } else {\n        auto rf1 \u003d f1[0];\n        SkDebugf(\"f1: [%f:%f] %s\\n\",\n                 rf1.rect.fLeft, rf1.rect.fRight,\n                 rf1.direction \u003d\u003d TextDirection::kRtl ? \"rtl\" : \"ltr\");\n    }\n\nwhich makes things more consistent and less surprising.",
